      <title>谷歌裁员并将部分职位转移到海外以削减成本</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/google-lays-off-employees-shifts-some-roles-abroad-amid-cost-cuts-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet 旗下的谷歌发言人周三表示，该公司正在裁员，具体人数不详，这是这家科技巨头为控制成本而进行的最新一次裁员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/google-lays-off-employees-shifts-some-roles-abroad-amid-cost-cuts-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 18:39:53 GMT</pubDate>
